            title: "Buy signal: Whales of BNB increased their holdings ",
            message_html: "The top 5 holders of Binance (BNB) <img src=\"#{image_path('signals/bnb.png')}\" /> increased their holdings from 10% to 12% overall in the last 24 hours.",
          } %>

